{"tid":2226932,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Made In Taiwan - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-10-02T11:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T11:46:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"626e711f2018a6b291825c06443aef28cdba7e8d","tid":2226932,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:16:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201002/VD5WYRYXFZES5CUHDATXUTVIYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201002%2FVD5WYRYXFZES5CUHDATXUTVIYU%2F&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdArTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=e105d202\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201002%2FVD5WYRYXFZES5CUHDATXUTVIYU%2F&h=f641762f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201002/VD5WYRYXFZES5CUHDATXUTVIYU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nMade In Taiwan - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Y2pPJ5XJ5DD34CuoZrOHLsD2cxQ=/1254x708/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LQQC2AZ4BFEAJFTWUCE2O7MPSA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FY2pPJ5XJ5DD34CuoZrOHLsD2cxQ%3D%2F1254x708%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLQQC2AZ4BFEAJFTWUCE2O7MPSA.png&h=df640348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為副董事長兼財務長孟晚舟引渡案，9月28日在加拿大再度開庭。台灣人很興奮地發現，中國華為公主出庭時，公開佩戴的淺紫色口罩，居然是Made In Taiwan！她不止對台灣防疫產品投信任一票，也投了品味一票。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大是買不到台灣口罩的，基本上，從大型連鎖超巿Costco，到蚊型家庭式雜貨鋪，從各大藥房到便利店，能夠買得到的即用即棄口罩，幾乎全部來自中國，只有少量可重複使用的布質口罩，在加拿大本地製造。而中國的口罩，只在包裝盒上標注產地，口罩上面，不會像台灣的口罩那樣印上Made In Taiwan字樣。中國製造的口罩不標注產地，自然有人人皆知的原因。不過，此時此刻，倒也算是一份體貼，若人人必須戴着Made In China的口罩在街上走，一定不好意思像孟晚舟那樣，在鏡頭前高仰脖頸，拂開長髮，驕傲地秀出產地。<br />\n<br />\n所以，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，精挑細選的。<br />\n<br />\n中國趁疫情大量輸出防疫用品，可是大量黑心商品、偽劣商品被多國退回，加拿大是其中一個受害國。四月份，加拿大政府宣佈從中國購買的100萬個KN95口罩不符標準，不會分派到各省巿。<br />\n<br />\n此後中國做了大量洗底工作，希望扭轉形象，沒想到華為公主卻在全世界人面前對中國製造四個字投不信任一票。連中國人都不相信中國產品，還有甚麼可說的？"},{"pid":"0bacfcdec7f4078f91a0915228b6f728f13d3f7f","tid":2226932,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />電話都係用IPHONE"},{"pid":"b0d04b4aec3759f570d5995df9d4a66e3de7f7e1","tid":2226932,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"係中囯國人一定明<br />\n<br />\n香港藍屍先以為自己明"}]}